lead_paragraph: A Brazilian judge ordered on Monday the release of a high-ranking IOC member who was arrested during the Rio de Janeiro Games in a ticket-scalping probe.

headline.print_headline: Brazil Judge Orders Release of IOC Member in Ticket Probe
